Tudo bem.

346
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:05,880
"Tudo bem" o quê?

347
00:32:09,080 --> 00:32:11,760
Sábado à noite, eu descobri que...

348
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:16,440
Carol e Daniel namoraram no verão.

349
00:32:24,760 --> 00:32:25,600
E daí?

350
